ps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224017739483/009.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dfde0f8a-7d08-49c7-99de-0d9a42d691b8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-59015cef-c93f-4de1-b397-cfaeec9abf24\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3e8e75a2-a1c6-48b5-a1da-bc14ca70c4f7\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">걸이형 단상자 제작 시 주의점</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-99d1ff2f-bd67-458f-9f4b-7a01672afc20\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fb108241-ad37-41ab-a7fc-3e255d3b992f\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d125c1c2-7221-4d9c-bbe9-b04f4d0d08cb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-baf883b1-da66-4776-88a7-24e55ec7cff0\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">□ 뚜껑의 위치와 방향을 헷갈리지 마십시오.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4d8afca0-c27c-499b-9d47-0f5b81373f96\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-abd7f2d5-8b33-4fa5-9bb4-43fd913e643e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">패키지 작업 시 아직도 방향과 위치를 혼동하는 사람이 있습니다. 물론 아직도 용도에 따라 뚜껑을 여는 방향이 앞쪽이다 뒤쪽이라고 논쟁하는 경우도 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a2779fcd-b3dd-4343-b91c-2962a4f659fa\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0e4c2440-03c6-4d03-a87e-3baeab7de86b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">분명한 건 걸이용으로 제작되는 끼운 부분은 정면 뒤쪽에 자라잡아야 하고 뚜껑은 정면에서 앞쪽으로 끼울 수 있도록 디자인해야 한다는 겁니다. 또한 정면에서 볼 때 접착면이 보이게 칼선을 만들지 않습니다. 이 부분이 잘 이해가 되지 않으시면 언제든 문의나 네이버 톡톡을 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F224017739483#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bbb95318-6564-4b7d-b02b-9ac40ce56014\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bcb4a8f9-136f-4953-a83a-e5015e88d0bf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6e644ea9-ebf3-492d-8e87-d7bdbbf73f72\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5e569571-dab5-4099-8a42-ce039ee174a7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3aa9a6c0-9382-490c-82cc-ccc1e5e4d08d\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">□ 접히는 부분을 접착을 할 수도 있고 앞쪽에 구멍을 내기도 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a8426339-6212-46bd-8777-e0c935f4e214\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e60433af-53a8-4064-8f94-6dd3cd2c9d19\" style=\"color:#555555;\">패키지는 어차피 목형을 만들기 때문에 자유롭게 모양을 만들 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-10a8a3de-e3bb-4bb2-9fa5-563aea889f59\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-438c9b7a-2fde-4354-8442-e7a2313ccdaa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그러므로 물건이 보이도록 앞쪽에 구멍을 내고 투명 PET를 접착하기도 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-97dcb96d-80e3-482d-bf83-671caf798787\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224017739483/010.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224017739483/011.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224017739483/012.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-a26084f4-3fa4-4a6c-89f9-188b10f6f1ab\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5b9bb061-d7dd-44e0-b586-cb1b99e42a2e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-7104f121-0e69-423b-bdf2-9215e24c460f\" style=\"\">수량이 많은 단상자는 반드시 샘플을 만들고 진행하시는 것이 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3dd522b0-ea6a-4c6c-91c4-1442fddaf4c0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d3f5df8b-83aa-4613-afc7-5ff7038220f5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ccab44a9-5496-4fad-9eec-8ffbbae94231\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄에서 한 번의 실수로 패키지 박스 전체를 버리거나 다시 만들어야 하는 경우도 매우 많습니다. 간단한 실수로 인해 큰 사고로 이어질 수 있습니다. 이런 사고를 방지하기 위해서는 반드시 시험 샘플을 만드시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4b848317-cd72-4088-a96f-1266c769b753\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b38fda3f-b964-4035-b87e-2b3b7a6e6fdb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8baede7f-919c-47ea-804d-7c78e907fc10\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a45f7f0e-a1ba-4885-a571-2bec5e528f3a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 소량의 단상자를 샘플로 제작해 드리고 있습니다. 물론 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-55f94829-bdae-4f31-b36e-a1b96f02cd05\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>본 작업이 보장되면 협의에 의해 무상으로도 샘플 제작이 가능</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5401ca0f-22c7-4ee7-af68-ad3875013e3c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fd6179d5-0357-49b1-8a09-1db634ab9b03\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c72d5334-fe47-44ec-8e64-79a44ae97189\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d290d1d8-db18-4323-96f9-2179c5dd71d9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1571ab2a-a756-4777-827f-a2824870b9fd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">납기가 급하다고 해서 샘플을 만들지 않고 진행하다 보면 반드시 사고가 날 확률도 있으니 시험 샘플은 반드시 제작하시기 권해드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8edeb53e-4b3c-426a-ba0f-a3ebdc1a0b57\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f0e1706d-e4f2-4b09-9751-d587199a10c0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-836c3b48-f2ac-4c27-935b-af78b9822b21\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7c3cf91a-a24c-495f-a027-e5c7b6e2092a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">특히 다음과 같은 분은 샘플 제작 후 본 작업을 진행하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f340e7c0-ae61-4c35-90bb-691f0bbaabe4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7f3e656b-428f-4e14-90e3-5aaa93bf7f57\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-250f4c66-56dc-4ebb-985f-7b633df86e1e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7205cc4b-fd12-424f-a5e2-8a82da9fd41a\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">□ 단상자나 패키지 박스를 처음 제작해 보시는 회사나 개인</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3a85b0db-2ad3-40cc-8481-538e41b03779\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-244b4a50-c26b-4663-bde7-36ab74bd884b\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">□ 수량이 많거나 일반적이지 않은 단상자 형태를 만드시는 분</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0746cc93-a6e8-455e-910a-09d0d9af3562\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-38f8138e-322e-4423-b66c-80102c36a8cf\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">□ 납기가 여유 있고 색상, 형태, 사이즈, 제품과의 궁합 등등을 먼저 알아보고 싶은 분</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5f4b48bd-860c-44eb-a5f1-5a6ccc84f946\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-393d3a5a-5abb-42fb-b30a-847ec1e488dc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7bd6f169-550c-46d8-a51a-c09e37c1559b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224017739483/013.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-364dcdda-6c07-42aa-a5f7-3f3628914ba6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224017739483/014.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-79eba2a2-27d6-46f0-a2d7-3e8b209e30d5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-31c83cab-ab04-4137-b68b-cc42c03862b8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-24ae41f1-f8fb-4147-9278-5edd398743cb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}